    <string name="welcome_message">Welcome to AgriSurvey!</string>
    <string name="app_introduction">AgriSurvey empowers farmers with easy-to-use surveys that capture real-time data about land size, irrigation, crops, and seasonal patterns. With this data, we generate clear visual insights to help you make informed choices every step of the way. \n\nWhether you\'re planning your next season, evaluating crop performance, or optimizing your irrigation strategy — AgriSurvey gives you the tools to farm smarter and more efficiently. \n\nStart your journey towards smarter farming today!</string>
